New design In App Notifications

You can now close a media file with a vertical swipe.

You can now send quickly messages from hidden chat lists to your default lists Deleted photo video in the chat also deletes them from the gallery Fixed that push notifications disappear automatically when you open Kedr Fixed when selected video for sending was just a black screen
Fixed problems with resending files.
Fixed push notofications Fixed sharing photos videos from other apps
Bug fixes

Bug fixes and improvements
Bug fixes: Fixed a problem with tapping a message for menu on some phones. You can swipe now message for quotation to both sides.
We have updated the design! You can now chose between three different themes!
In this version we have two new functions: you can now share messages from Kedr to other messengers you reply to messages in your chats

You can now voluntarily add your telephone number so you can be found easily by your contacts. You can also see which of your contacts has registered their telephone number.
You can now voluntarily add your telephone number so you can be found easily by your contacts. You can also see which of your contacts has registered their telephone number.

Added optional preview in push notification Go directly to chat by tapping on push notification Added all contacts to send invite Fixed bug with hiding keyboard Fixed bug with contact transfer Fixed bugs with deleting messages and chats Intro for hidden lists will be shown only once Fixed bug with custom names in call list
We have update the design and fixed some bugs! Receive your given contact name in the push messages!
We have reworked our hidden lists to make a better experience for you!

We have added hidden contact lists. You can create lists where you can hide chats and contacts so nobody can see them even if your phone is unlocked! You can mute contacts and move them across the lists.
Bug fixes and performance improvements.

You can see now in the chat the online status of your contact. You can change the chat tab last message preview to a neutral message. You can remove the message preview for all contacts and groups in the chat tab. You can change the photos of your contacts. Bug fixes and performance improvements.
